Ok, so Nathan "NateDGreat" Ayres lives in Louisville, Kentucky. I live in Owensboro, Kentucky. I visit Louisville multiple times a year.
I am moving to England next summer to attend the University of Nottingham and major in CS (not that it matters :stuck_out_tongue: )
I will only be visiting Louisville a few more times before I move... I must meet the great Nate.
Nate, wherever you are, ...I want to meet you, in a non-creepy fan way :retard:
